  "detailed_description": "Become a sheriff and find all the cats wanted in the Wild West!<br>Explore the funny doodle-style artwork as you embark on a quest to find over 600 naughty cats hidden throughout the game!<br>Test your attention and observation skills in this fun, relaxing hidden object game.<br>Can you catch all the cats?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2545570/extras/089971002141f0689d1e8aa1dde18a77.poster.avif?t=1773083832\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2545570/extras/089971002141f0689d1e8aa1dde18a77.webm?t=1773083832\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2545570/extras/089971002141f0689d1e8aa1dde18a77.mp4?t=1773083832\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>KEY FEATURES:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Several hundred hand-drawn funny objects<br></li><li> Dozens of funny \"mouth-made\" sounds<br></li><li> 15 levels <br></li><li> Over 600 cats to find <br></li><li> 45 secrets<br></li><li> Over 2 hours of great entertainment<br></li><li> Created by passionate and experienced indie games creators<br></li><li> Great music full of nostalgia, relaxation, and humor<br></li><li> Excellent value for money </li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2545570/extras/eb3069506be394dcf958663aa7dd2df6.poster.avif?t=1773083832\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2545570/extras/eb3069506be394dcf958663aa7dd2df6.webm?t=1773083832\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2545570/extras/eb3069506be394dcf958663aa7dd2df6.mp4?t=1773083832\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
